  keywords = {Aggravation of organic pollution and Eutrophication,BACTERIAL DIVERSITY,CHONGMING DONGTAN,ENZYME-ACTIVITIES,MICROBIAL COMMUNITY,ORGANIC-MATTER,RIBOSOMAL-RNA,SALT-MARSH,Sea-level rise,Soil carbon turnover,Soil heterotrophic and autotrophic microbial activities,Soil microbial community,SP NOV.,SULFUR-OXIDIZING GAMMAPROTEOBACTERIUM,Yangtze River estuary,YANGTZE-RIVER ESTUARY}
